 The Chief Whip of the House of Representatives, Hon. Mohammed Tahir Monguno, has congratulated Governor Babagana Umara Zulum of Borno State as he marks his 50th birthday. Monguno, who represents Marte/Monguno/Nganzai Federal Constituency of Borno State in the House, said Governor Zulum has lived a life worthy of emulation. Yakassai blasts Ezeife over 2023 presidency 3 killed, dozens kidnapped as gunmen waylay 14-seater bus on… N100m concession agreement: Malami moves to avert another… Monthly sanitation: Anambra govt to establish mobile courts… In a statement made available to news men in Abuja, Monguno wished Governor Zulum continued protection from the Almighty Allah as well as guidance for him to pilot the affairs of the state for the benefit of the Borno people. According to him, “I wish to congratulate my Governor, His Excellency Governor Babagana Umara Zulum, for clocking 50. His new age calls for a lot of prayers for him to succeed in his leadership in Borno State. “I pray that Almighty Allah will give him the wisdom and the strength to take Borno State to greater heights”. The Chief Whip who doubles as the Leader of the Northeast Caucus in the House described Governor Zulum as a dedicated leader, who has good plans for Borno State in the next four years.  SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE
